{
  "name": "ZenTrade — Support Agent",
  "_instrucciones": [
    "ANTES DE IMPORTAR — reemplaza estos 3 valores:",
    "1. TU_SUPPORT_AGENT_SECRET → el string que pusiste en .env.local como SUPPORT_AGENT_SECRET",
    "2. TU_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID    → tu chat ID de Telegram (ver instrucciones abajo)",
    "3. Conecta las credenciales IMAP y SMTP cuando n8n te las pida al importar",
    "",
    "CÓMO OBTENER TU TELEGRAM CHAT ID:",
    "  1. En Telegram busca @userinfobot",
    "  2. Mándale cualquier mensaje",
    "  3. Te responde con tu ID (un número como 123456789)"
  ],
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "node-imap-trigger",
      "name": "Email Trigger (IMAP)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailReadImap",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [240, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "mailbox": "INBOX",
        "downloadAttachments": false,
        "format": "simple",
        "options": {}
      },
      "credentials": {
        "imap": {
          "id": "CONECTAR_EN_N8N",
          "name": "Hostinger IMAP"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-extract",
      "name": "Extraer datos del email",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [460, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const email = items[0].json;\n\nconst fromRaw = email.from ?? '';\nconst fromMatch = fromRaw.match(/<(.+?)>/);\nconst fromEmail = fromMatch ? fromMatch[1] : fromRaw.trim();\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    from: fromEmail,\n    fromRaw: fromRaw,\n    subject: email.subject ?? '(sin asunto)',\n    body: (email.text ?? email.html ?? '').replace(/<[^>]*>/g, '').slice(0, 3000),\n    messageId: email.messageId ?? ''\n  }\n}];"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-http",
      "name": "Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4,
      "position": [680, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://www.zen-trader.com/api/agents/support",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "Bearer TU_SUPPORT_AGENT_SECRET"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "contentType": "json",
        "body": {
          "from": "={{ $json.from }}",
          "subject": "={{ $json.subject }}",
          "body": "={{ $json.body }}"
        },
        "options": {
          "timeout": 30000
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-if",
      "name": "¿Auto-responder o escalar?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [900, 300],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": false,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-auto-reply",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.shouldAutoReply }}",
              "rightValue": true,
              "operator": {
                "type": "boolean",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-send-reply",
      "name": "Enviar respuesta automática",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1120, 160],
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "support@zen-trader.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.from }}",
        "subject": "=Re: {{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.subject }}",
        "emailFormat": "text",
        "text": "={{ $('Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)').item.json.reply }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "credentials": {
        "smtp": {
          "id": "CONECTAR_EN_N8N",
          "name": "Hostinger SMTP"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-telegram",
      "name": "Notificar escalación en Telegram",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegram",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1120, 440],
      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "TU_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID",
        "text": "=🚨 *Soporte ZenTrade — Revisar*\n\n*De:* {{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.fromRaw }}\n*Asunto:* {{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.subject }}\n*Categoría:* {{ $('Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)').item.json.category }}\n*Razón:* {{ $('Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)').item.json.escalationReason }}\n\n*Draft sugerido:*\n{{ $('Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)').item.json.draft }}",
        "additionalFields": {
          "parse_mode": "Markdown"
        }
      },
      "credentials": {
        "telegramApi": {
          "id": "CONECTAR_EN_N8N",
          "name": "ZenTrade Telegram Bot"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "node-draft-email",
      "name": "Enviar draft a tu propio correo",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1340, 440],
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "support@zen-trader.com",
        "toEmail": "support@zen-trader.com",
        "subject": "=[DRAFT] Re: {{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.subject }}",
        "emailFormat": "text",
        "text": "=--- DRAFT PARA REVISAR Y REENVIAR ---\nPara: {{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.fromRaw }}\n\n{{ $('Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)').item.json.draft }}\n\n---\nEmail original:\n{{ $('Extraer datos del email').item.json.body }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "credentials": {
        "smtp": {
          "id": "CONECTAR_EN_N8N",
          "name": "Hostinger SMTP"
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Email Trigger (IMAP)": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Extraer datos del email", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Extraer datos del email": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "Llamar al Support Agent (ZenTrade API)": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "¿Auto-responder o escalar?", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    },
    "¿Auto-responder o escalar?": {
      "main": [
        [{ "node": "Enviar respuesta automática", "type": "main", "index": 0 }],
        [{ "node": "Notificar escalación en Telegram", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]
      ]
    },
    "Notificar escalación en Telegram": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Enviar draft a tu propio correo", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  }
}
